Speculum Scripturale Schiſmaticorum: OR, A SCRIPTURE LOOKING—GLASSE, MOST EXACTLY CHARACTERIZING ALL SORTS OF SCHISMATICKS: Wherein,
As, in a Looking-Glaſs, Face anſwers Face;
So, Scriptures paint Seducers Root and Race:
And, that they are the Seedſmen of all Evil;
And, muſt be ſhun'd, as Serpents, or the Devil.
